{
  "video_id": "Mpo6rgvOVGc",
  "title": "The Programmer Who Invented Ctrl+Alt+Del",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 980.0,
      "end_time": 3630.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] This is the IBM Personal Computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3630.0,
      "end_time": 7529.0,
      "text": "It was the most advanced computing machine ever created."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7530.0,
      "end_time": 9990.0,
      "text": "However, this isn't a story about a computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9990.0,
      "end_time": 12810.0,
      "text": "but a story about when a computer stops working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12810.0,
      "end_time": 15520.0,
      "text": "and the man who created a way to start it all over;"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15520.0,
      "end_time": 19551.0,
      "text": "the man who invented Control + Alt + Delete."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19551.0,
      "end_time": 22166.0,
      "text": "(chiming music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22167.0,
      "end_time": 23170.0,
      "text": "(exciting music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23170.0,
      "end_time": 24213.0,
      "text": "Let's get into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26170.0,
      "end_time": 28340.0,
      "text": "[Dave] Hi, I'm Dr. Dave Bradley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28340.0,
      "end_time": 30830.0,
      "text": "but you can call me Dr. Dave."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 30830.0,
      "end_time": 35129.0,
      "text": "Back in 1980, I worked on the IBM Personal Computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35130.0,
      "end_time": 37560.0,
      "text": "My particular job on the IBM PC"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 37560.0,
      "end_time": 40511.0,
      "text": "was writing the basic input-output system."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40511.0,
      "end_time": 42980.0,
      "text": "(clicking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42980.0,
      "end_time": 44489.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] Even with an elite team"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 44490.0,
      "end_time": 47217.0,
      "text": "of engineers and designers, not everything goes smoothly"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47217.0,
      "end_time": 48963.0,
      "text": "when you're building a computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50980.0,
      "end_time": 53699.0,
      "text": "[Dave] We had programs that ran most of the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 53700.0,
      "end_time": 56790.0,
      "text": "but when they failed the only way to reset the system"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56790.0,
      "end_time": 58407.0,
      "text": "was turn the power off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 58407.0,
      "end_time": 59459.0,
      "text": "(clock ticking) wait a while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 59460.0,
      "end_time": 61200.0,
      "text": "turn the power back on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 61200.0,
      "end_time": 63500.0,
      "text": "and it would go through a very long self test."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 64839.0,
      "end_time": 68453.0,
      "text": "But the system might die every five to 10 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 69940.0,
      "end_time": 71649.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] What he needed was a way to shortcut"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71650.0,
      "end_time": 75260.0,
      "text": "the restart process. (beeping)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 76880.0,
      "text": "[Dave] One of the things we discussed"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 76880.0,
      "end_time": 79200.0,
      "text": "was putting a reset button on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 79200.0,
      "end_time": 80759.0,
      "text": "But if you put it on the system board,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 80760.0,
      "end_time": 82860.0,
      "text": "there was a chance that you could hit it by mistake"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 82860.0,
      "end_time": 85920.0,
      "text": "and all your data gets lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 85920.0,
      "end_time": 87789.0,
      "text": "(upbeat electronic music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 87790.0,
      "end_time": 91272.0,
      "text": "So what we did was came up with a three-key sequence"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91272.0,
      "end_time": 93520.0,
      "text": "that would reset the computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93520.0,
      "end_time": 95703.0,
      "text": "and you couldn't hit by mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 97600.0,
      "end_time": 100380.0,
      "text": "A single Control key, a single Alt key,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100380.0,
      "end_time": 102920.0,
      "text": "and then, all the way over at the right-hand side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 102920.0,
      "end_time": 104143.0,
      "text": "a single Delete key."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 105370.0,
      "end_time": 107290.0,
      "text": "You hit that Control + Alt + Delete,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 108760.0,
      "end_time": 110959.0,
      "text": "you're deleting everything that you're working on right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110959.0,
      "end_time": 113980.0,
      "text": "and starting new."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113980.0,
      "end_time": 116410.0,
      "text": "I was also able to skip over many of the tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116410.0,
      "end_time": 119119.0,
      "text": "so instead of taking a minute or two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119120.0,
      "end_time": 120873.0,
      "text": "it was 10 or 15 seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 122940.0,
      "end_time": 125649.0,
      "text": "But it wasn't a big deal at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 125650.0,
      "end_time": 129680.0,
      "text": "It was like number 17 on the list of 100 different things I had to fix."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 132440.0,
      "end_time": 133870.0,
      "text": "[Narrator] Even though it was built only as a development tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 135700.0,
      "end_time": 136940.0,
      "text": "programmers began incorporating the feature into their applications."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 140100.0,
      "end_time": 142359.0,
      "text": "From there it was released into the wild,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 142360.0,
      "end_time": 145304.0,
      "text": "but didn't immediately reach pop culture status."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 145304.0,
      "end_time": 146560.0,
      "text": "(bomb whistling) - [Dave] For years"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146560.0,
      "end_time": 148300.0,
      "text": "it was no big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 148300.0,
      "end_time": 151671.0,
      "text": "And then at the 20th anniversary of the IBM PC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 151671.0,
      "end_time": 155220.0,
      "text": "that's when Control + Alt + Delete"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 155220.0,
      "end_time": 157669.0,
      "text": "became sort of a cultural icon."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 157669.0,
      "end_time": 159660.0,
      "text": "(exploding) (screeching)"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 159660.0,
      "end_time": 162472.0,
      "text": "It was the simplest and easiest way to fix your problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 164144.0,
      "end_time": 168830.0,
      "text": "Hit Control + Alt + Delete and start all over."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 170400.0,
      "end_time": 171739.0,
      "text": "(tape rewinding)"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 171740.0,
      "end_time": 173729.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Despite all this, Dr. Dave doesn't think much"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 173729.0,
      "end_time": 176670.0,
      "text": "of this contribution to computing history."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176670.0,
      "end_time": 178959.0,
      "text": "- [Dave] I did lots of things with IBM,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 178960.0,
      "end_time": 181890.0,
      "text": "but all everybody remembers is Control + Alt + Delete."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 181890.0,
      "end_time": 183890.0,
      "text": "But, I'll take that."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 183900.0,
      "end_time": 185350.0,
      "text": "The fame of Control + Alt + Delete"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 185350.0,
      "end_time": 189100.0,
      "text": "means that I worked on a very successful product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 189100.0,
      "end_time": 192850.0,
      "text": "and I'm very proud of having been able to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 192860.0,
      "end_time": 195503.0,
      "text": "(fun instrumental music)"
    }
  ]
}